summary: just some small changes to the nightingale armor(not a replacer!!)
descriptionHtml:
Small changes to the Nightingale Armor

hood changed to add bow damage 
cruises changed to ebony mail effect 
and gloves changed to shrouded gloves
Boots stayed the same 

can be found in the solitude house in the \"tainted cupboard\"
Must purchase the house ad all of its upgrades 


Also, no I am not going to tell you were it is in the house, just look for it
author: ThrashLord
